			</header>
			<section id="content">	
				<h3>Voice Commands</h3>
				<ul class="settingslist">
					<li>Say <b>Next</b> in cooking mode to go to next step</li>
					<p><br></p>
					<li>Say <b>Previous</b> in cooking mode to go to previous step</li>
					<p><br></p>
					<li>Say <b>Listen</b> in cooking mode hear the step</li>
					<br>
				</ul>
				<h3>Add/Remove Recipe</h3>
				<ul class="settingslist">
					<li> Remove Recipe</li>
					<li>1. Go to <b>My Recipes</b> (book icon)</li>
					<li>2. Click on the recipe</li>
					<li>3. Click <b>Remove Recipe</b></li>
					<br>
					<li>Add Recipe</li>
					<li>1. Click on the recipe</li>
					<li>2. Click on <b>Add Recipe</b></li> 
					<li>3. It will be added to <b>My Recipes</b></li>
				</ul>
			</section>
